2.	Conduct a semestral physical count of inventory items by type and submit the results to the Inventory Committee.

c.	Direct the MHO to provide the Accounting Office of the monthly report on receipt, issuance and balances of vaccines and other inventories directly received from outside sources to serve as the basis in recording the inventories in the books of the LGU; and

d.	Direct the Inventory Committee to conduct periodic physical inventory of supplies semestrally and to prepare and submit RPCI (See Appendix R) to the Audit Team.

