Submit copy of the Memorandum of Agreement which clearly defines that the project is beyond LGU’s capacity to undertake including attachment of appropriate documents to liquidate the fund transfers to other LGU’s and local parish, otherwise, adjust the expense accounts to Due from other LGU’s/NGOs; and
Submit justification and other appropriate documents to support those programs/projects classified in Annexes I to Q whose purpose/s clearly not falling under the types of projects that should be under the 20% (DF).

